function loadMoreCollections(seo_alias, page = 1, callback, hasfilter = true,limit = null) {
let request = '';
let color = '';
let query = location.search.replace(/\?/g, '');
let hash = location.hash.replace(/#/g, '');
let search = [request, color, query, hash].filter(Boolean).join('&');

let url = '';
let _limit = limit ? '&limit=' + limit : '';
if (hasfilter) {
url = `/collections/load-more?random=true&page=${page}&seo_alias=${seo_alias}${search ? `&${search}` : ''}${_limit}`
} else {
url = `/collections/load-more?random=true&page=${page}&seo_alias=${seo_alias}${_limit}`
}
$.ajax({
url: url,
type: 'GET',
success: function(response) {
callback(response);
}
});
}


function indexLoadMoreCollections(seo_alias, params, page = 1, callback) {
let request = '';
let color = '';
let query = location.search.replace(/\?/g, '');
let hash = location.hash.replace(/#/g, '');
let search = [request, color, query, hash, ...params].filter(Boolean).join('&');
$.ajax({
url: `${window.location.origin}/collection/products?random=true&seo_alias=${seo_alias}&page=${page}&limit=25&thumbnail=375_425${search ? `&${search}` : ''}`,
type: 'GET',
success: function(response) {
callback(response);
}
});
}

function filterRedirect(seo_alias, params, params_current = [], remove = '', remove_all = false) {
let atts = [];

// toan bo att
let map_atts = [];
atts.forEach((att) => {
Object.values(att.items).forEach((item) => {
map_atts.push(`att[${att.seo_alias}]=${item.seo_alias}`)
})
})

// nhung att se khong noi slug
let att_not_concat = [];
params = params.filter(e => {
return !e.includes('itm') && !e.includes('utm');
})
//lay param
let param = params.filter((e) => {
let att = e.split("=")[0] || '';
return (e.includes("att[") && !att_not_concat.includes(att)) || e.includes("color");
});

let search = params.filter((e) => !param.includes(e));

let path = '/collection/' + seo_alias;

let is_reload = location.pathname == path;

let hash = location.hash.replace(/^#/, '') + '&' + search.join('&');
hash = hash.split('&').filter(Boolean);

// remove double
let hash_key = []
let hash_tmp = [];
hash.forEach(e => {
let [key, value] = e.split('=');
if(hash_key.includes(key)) {
hash_tmp = hash_tmp.map(x => {
return x.includes(key) ? e : x;
})
} else {
hash_key.push(key);
hash_tmp.push(e);
}
})

hash = hash_tmp;

if (remove_all) {
history.pushState({}, '', `${path}${location.search}#${params.join('&')}`);
location.reload();
return;
}

if (remove) {
let concat = location.pathname.replace(path, '').replace(/^-/, '');
// TH xoá thuộc phần nối url, kiểm tra hash có attr thì nối vào
if (concat && remove.includes(concat)) {
let new_concat = '';
let new_hash = [];
hash.forEach(e => {
// nếu chưa có phần nối mới và trong hash có att
if (!new_concat && (e.includes('att[') || e.includes('color'))) {
new_concat = e.split('=')[1];
} else {
new_hash.push(e);
}
})
new_concat = new_concat ? '-' + new_concat : '';
history.pushState({}, '', `${path}${new_concat}${location.search}#${new_hash.join('&')}`);
location.reload();
return;
}

//TH xoá thuộc hash
let new_hash = hash.filter(e => {
let [key, val] = e.split('=');
let [key_remove, val_remove] = remove.split('=');
key = key.replace('att[', '').replace(']', '');
key_remove = key_remove.replace('att[', '').replace(']', '');

return !(val === val_remove && (key_remove.includes(key) || key.includes(key_remove)))
})
history.pushState({}, '', `${location.pathname}${location.search}#${new_hash.join('&')}`);
location.reload();
return;
}

// Khoong thay doi thuoc tinh
if(!param.length) {
history.pushState({}, '', `${location.pathname}${location.search}#${hash.join('&')}`);
location.reload();
return;
}

// TH URL chưa được nối
if (is_reload) {
param = param.map(e => {
return e.split('=')[1];
});

history.pushState({}, '', `${path}${param.length ? '-'+ param.join('-') : ''}${location.search}#${hash.join('&')}`);
location.reload();
return;
}

// TH URL nối thay đổi
let concat = location.pathname.replace(path, '').replace(/^-/, '');
// cần biết đuọc key của thuộc tính đc nối
let key_attr = map_atts.filter(e => {
return !att_not_concat.includes(e.split('=')[0]) && e.includes(concat);
}).map(e => {
return e.split('=')[0];
})[0] || '';

if (!key_attr) {
let colors = [];
colors = colors.filter(x => x.seo_alias.includes(concat))
if(colors.length) {
key_attr = 'color';
}
}

// nếu chứa key attr thì thay thế url
if(key_attr && param[0].includes(key_attr)) {
param = param.map(e => {
return e.split('=')[1];
});
location.href = `${path}-${param.join('-')}${location.search}#${hash.join('&')}`;
return;
}

// param = param.map(e => {
// return e.replace('att[', '').replace(']', '');
// });
param.forEach(e => {
let [key, value] = e.split('=');
if(hash_key.includes(key)) {
hash = hash.map(x => {
return x.includes(key) ? e : x;
})
} else {
hash.push(e);
}
})
history.pushState({}, '', `${location.pathname}${location.search}#${hash.join('&')}`);
location.reload();
}

$.ajax({
url: 'https://www.coolmate.me/wishlistcoupon' + '?coupon=' + coupon + '&redirect=0',
type: "GET",
cache: false,
}).done(function(res) {

if (res.success) {

message: res.message,
level: 'message'
})
}
}).fail(() => {
theme.Loading.hide();
theme.PushNotify({
message: 'Lưu mã thất bại!',
level: 'error'
})
}).always(() => {
theme.Loading.hide()
})
}

const valid = theme.validateEmail(value);
const _error = $(this).parents('form').find('[rel-script="claim-error"]');

if(!valid) {
_error.html('Email không đúng!');
return;
}else{
const API_URL = `${window.location.origin}/lixi-coupon`;

// _popup.find('.popup-claim__confirm').html('');
$.ajax({
url: API_URL,
type: "GET",
dataType: "json",
data: {
email: value
},
}).done(function(res) {
const {success,message,discount_code,start_date,end_date,detail,image,discount_type} = res;
_popup.removeClass('active-loading');
if(success) {
theme.setCookie('check_is_popup_claim_2023','true',999);
theme.setCookie('check_is_popup__claim','true',999);
saveCode(discount_code);
const claim = $('.popup-claim__success');
claim.find('[rel-script="claim-coupon"]').html(discount_code);
claim.find('[rel-script="claim-coupon"]').attr('data-coupon2',discount_code);
claim.children('[rel-script="data-date"]').html('HSD: ' + start_date + ' - ' + end_date );
claim.find('[rel-script="claim-form-img"]').attr('src',image);
$('.popup-claim__confirm').remove();
$('.popup-claim__success').addClass('is-active');
if(discount_type == 'giveaway_product') {
$('.popup-claim__success').addClass('gift');
}else {
$('.popup-claim__success').removeClass('gift');
}
}else{
_error.html(message);
}
});
}
});
})
